-- dup on linear Array
[1 2 3] dup free free
-- dup on linear Record
{'x 1} dup free free
-- dup on linear Quotation
(1 plus) dup free free
-- drop on linear Array (use free instead)
[1 2 3] drop
-- drop on linear Record (use free instead)
{'x 1} drop
-- drop on linear Quotation (use free instead)
(1 plus) drop
-- borrow escape: identity quot leaks linear ref
[1 2 3] box () borrow free free
-- if branches produce different types
true () (drop 1) (drop 'hello) if drop
-- wrong argument type for plus
true 1 plus drop
-- undefined word
1 frobnicate
-- cons element type doesn't match array
true [1 2 3] cons free
-- set with wrong type for box contents
42 box true set free
-- double free on box
42 box 'b let b free b free
-- use after free on box
42 box 'b let b free b clone nip drop
-- float where int expected
1.0 2 plus drop
-- int where float expected
1 2.0 fadd drop
-- fmul with mixed types
1.0 2 fmul drop
-- sort on linear array elements (records not sortable)
[{'x 1}] sort free
-- filter on linear elements (dup requires Copy)
[{'x 1}] (true) filter free
-- sqrt on Int (expects Float)
4 sqrt drop
-- rise on linear elements
[[1] [2]] rise free free
-- replicate on linear elements
[[1] [2]] [1 1] replicate free
-- classify on linear elements
[[1] [2]] classify free free
-- pow on Int (expects Float)
2 3 pow drop
-- fgt on Int (expects Float)
1 2 fgt drop
